All Honks Day April 1st - YOTC - Graffiti - Hacking - Pirates - Street Art (CLOWNSEC)

Clownsec and The Clown Army are teaming up with several groups to create ultimate April 1st this year! A day of fun filled pranks which aim to make the world a BETTER place! ALL HONKS DAY BITCHES! 

Official Video For #AllHonksDay April 1st 2014
www . youtube . com / v=5n0vEfr9klM


------

It only takes one of you silly phucks to change the planet. See: Thepiratebay, Banksy, Negativland, Toy Punks, Geeks and Phreaks. Bringing you art, entertainment and otherwise filling your life with joy at the risk of their own freedom. They are to be cherished, appreciated, and are inspiring. Show the world what YOU are capable of.

The city is a one way conversation screaming at you, BUY BUY BUY, OBEY OBEY!
Is it not time to join the conversation? HONK THE PLANET!

- Compiled By An Anonymous Clown
